@startuml
!include ../../style.puml

participant "Client" as Client
participant "Process" as Process
participant "RequestWaitingList" as WaitingList
participant "Network" as Network

note over WaitingList
Tracks in-flight requests
by correlation id and timeout ticks.
end note

' [step1 {"name":"Client Starts Request"}]
Client -> Process : start request
' [/step1]

' [step2 {"name":"Register Waiting Request"}]
Process -> WaitingList : add(correlationId, timeout=3)
' [/step2]

' [step3 {"name":"Send Message"}]
Process -> Network : send(request)
' [/step3]

' [step4 {"name":"Tick Waiting List"}]
Process -> Process : tick()
Process -> WaitingList : tick()
WaitingList -> WaitingList : decrement timeout
' [/step4]

' [step5 {"name":"Response Arrives"}]
Network --> Process : response(correlationId)
' [/step5]

' [step6 {"name":"Complete And Remove"}]
Process -> WaitingList : complete(correlationId)
WaitingList --> Process : remove pending request
Process --> Client : success
' [/step6]

' [step7 {"name":"If No Response Arrives", "newPage":"true"}]
Process -> WaitingList : tick() ... tick() ... tick()
WaitingList --> Process : timeout(correlationId)
Process --> Client : timeout / fail
' [/step7]

note over Process, WaitingList
The waiting list tracks in-flight requests use tick based timeout.
end note

@enduml
